imdb.plot outline: It's a TV show about a TV show about Austin, Texas. Former musician Troy Dillinger is on a mission to share the best entertainment from Austin with the rest of the world on The Austin Variety Show. With no experience and no budget, he's the show's biggest supporter - and it's biggest liability. See great live music, comedy, burlesque, and an audience participation game show from "The Live Music Capital of the World" in a raw, raunchy stage show which is shot in Austin Variety Show's studios.
imdb.title: Austin Variety Show
